    <div style="margin-top: 80px;">
        <h2>Interesting Facts about Varsity</h2>
        <div>
            <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0;">Schools In or Near Varsity</h3>
            <p>If you are relocating to Varsity with your kids, you will be pleased to know that Varsity is in close proximity to several schools. Many of these are within walking distance of the neighbourhood and do not require you to travel long distances.</p>
            <h4>Elementary Schools</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Varsity Acres School</li>
                <li>Brentwood School</li>
                <li>Marion Carson School</li>
            </ul>
            <h4>Middle and High Schools</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>F. E. Osborne School</li>
