        <h2>FAQs about Varsity Real Estate and Neighborhood</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>
                <h3>Where do I get groceries?</h3>
                <p>Shop for groceries at Safeway Market Mall, where you can find organic fruits and vegetables, a deli, a bakery, and more. You can also shop at Planet Organic Health Corp, located on Varsity Drive. For international foods, you can visit the Filipiniana Store, where there is a variety of Filipino and other Asian grocery items.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>What is the best place to go shopping in Varsity?</h3>
                <p>CF Market Mall, one of the biggest malls in Calgary, is situated in Varsity. The mall has hundreds of retailers, a playground for kids and a food court. You can also visit the Shaganappi Village Shopping Centre for fresh, organic produce and clothing items. Northland Village is another shopping mall where you can purchase accessories, gifts, and high-quality apparel.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>What’s the best nearby restaurant?</h3>
                <p>Depending on your preference, there are different restaurants that serve delicious cuisine in Calgary. Matador Pizza, Varsity Pizza & Subs, and Vietnamese Chop Chop are some well-known restaurants in the community. A bit farther you can visit Euphoria Cafe and Snow Palace Restaurant.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>How do I get around? Public transportation, etc.?</h3>
                <p>The public transportation system in Varsity is among the most convenient and affordable ways of getting around. You can learn more about the local Public Transit and stops here.</p>
                <p>In addition, having your own bike or car would be useful in getting around to places. You can also use several different ridesharing services if you do not own a car.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>What’s the closest hospital?</h3>
                <p>Foothills Medical Centre is one of the closest hospitals near Varsity. For issues involving children’s health, Alberta Children’s Hospital is nearby within a few miles. You may also seek emergency care services at Sheldon M. Chumir Health Centre.</p>
            </li>

        </ol>
